itness to a supernatural murder.</p><p> “Together with the pragmatic and scientific townie, Velma, and the strange, but ever-so-handsome new kid, Freddy, they set out to solve the case that is pulling each of them into a creepy nightmare that threatens to expose all of their secrets.”</p><p> Josh Appelbaum and Scott Rosenberg are on board as showrunners and executive producers via their company Midnight Radio, whose previous projects include the <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/zo-kravitz">Zoë Kravitz</a> -starring <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/zoe-kravitz-says-high-fidelity-cancellation-was-a-big-mistake-3162042"><i>High Fidelity</i></a> series, sci-fi drama <i>From</i> and another Netflix live-action adaptation, <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/tv-reviews/cowboy-bebop-review-netflix-anime-3096762"><i>Cowboy Bebop</i></a> .</p><p> It will also be produced by Greg Berlanti, who oversaw <a href="https://www.nme.com/series/riverdale"><i>Riverdale</i></a> and <a href="https://www.nme.com/series/chilling-adventures-of-sabrina"><i>Chilling Adventures Of Sabrina</i></a> for the streaming platform, as well as Penn Badgley stalker series <a href="https://www.nme.com/series/you"><i>You</i></a> . </p><figure id="attachment_3849697" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3849697" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3849697" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/greg-berlanti.jpg" alt="Greg Berlanti attends the 'Fly Me To The Moon' world premiere in July, 2024. CREDIT: Dimitrios Kambouris via Getty Images." width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/greg-berlanti.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/greg-berlanti-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/greg-berlanti-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/greg-berlanti-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content