//www.nme.com/news/music/thom-yorke-shares-menacing-live-performance-of-back-in-the-game-collab-with-mark-pritchard-3843776">shared a live version of &#39;Back In The Game&#39;, recorded in Sydney</a> earlier this month.</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/mark-pritchard-and-thom-yorke-announce-tall-tales-special-screening-event-3849689">Mark Pritchard and Thom Yorke announce &#39;Tall Tales&#39; special screening event</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
